data.description: Welcome to this elegant Silvio model by Oakwood Homes in the stunning community of Banning Lewis Ranch. This home offers a convenient, low-maintenance and modern design. As you enter the home, you’ll be greeted with a thoughtfully designed open living space that seamlessly transitions into the dining and kitchen with a powder bath tucked away discreetly next to the stairs. The tasteful and modern kitchen is a homeowner’s dream with 42” upper cabinetry and rollouts in the base cabinetry, maximizing storage and making organization a breeze! You’ll also find gorgeous granite counter tops, ceramic tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and an island with counter height seating for four, perfect for hosting off the kitchen! Up the stairs you’ll discover the primary bedroom illuminated with natural light, and an ensuite bath. Down the hall you’ll be delighted to find a bonus room with endless possibilities, the second and third bedroom, as well as a laundry room and the third bathroom. Off the kitchen, towards the rear of the home you’ll find the two-car garage with ample parking. With the luxury of all Banning Lewis Ranch has to offer its residents, you’ll find yourself overjoyed with activities and amenities. Explore over 75 acres of parks, trails and open space, or take a trip to the Northtree Ranch House to find a junior Olympic pool, splash pad, and fitness center with high-tech equipment and free weights wall to wall. The list goes on with the Vista Water Park, a dog park, tennis courts, basketball courts, soccer and baseball fields, a rock-climbing area and so much more! Welcome to your oasis!
